        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_053_000083",
    "sentence": "十六年，以本職兼領振武節度使。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "十六年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_053_000084",
    "sentence": "時王師據德勝渡，汴軍據楊村渡在上流。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_053_000085",
    "sentence": "汴人運洛陽竹木，造浮橋以濟軍。",
    "entities": [
