    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_053_000093",
    "sentence": "汴軍退，加檢校太傅。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_053_000094",
    "sentence": "王師討張文禮於鎮州，閻寶、李嗣昭相次不利而歿。",
    "entities": [
